fields.value: Technology, Income Distribution and Poverty in the Philippines

authorName.value: Hossain, M., Gascon, F. and Marciano, E.

dsDescriptionValue.value: The study is based on village full enumeration field surveys. The main purpose of the study is to examine the changes in the structure of rural household income and its distribution over the past decade with primary data generated through in-depth household surveys in four villages with contrasting production environments. This study also shed light on the changes in the poverty situation of rural households over the 1985-97 period.

keywordValue.value: Production environments, input-output of rice production, price, wages, sources of income and poverty indicators
